{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"17bbdc92-dbd6-46bc-abfc-224746c90c2f","content":"Here's what you need for automatic crash dump collection with NativeAOT:\n\n**Environment variables** for your container spec:\n\n```yaml\nenv:\n  # Enable automatic crash dumps\n  - name: DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump\n    value: \"1\"\n  # Full dump (use \"2\" for heap-only, \"1\" for mini)\n  - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType\n    value: \"4\"\n  # Point to your createdump binary (required for NativeAOT)\n  - name: DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath\n    value: \"/opt/tools/createdump\"\n  # Dump file path — %p=PID, %t=timestamp\n  - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName\n    value: \"/tmp/dumps/coredump.%p.%t\"\n  # Optional: enable createdump diagnostics logging\n  - name: DOTNET_CreateDumpDiagnostics\n    value: \"1\"\n  # Optional: generate a companion JSON crash report\n  - name: DOTNET_EnableCrashReport\n    value: \"1\"\n```\n\n**Volume for dump storage** — add to the pod spec:\n\n```yaml\nspec:\n  containers:\n    - name: your-app\n      # ... env from above ...\n      volumeMounts:\n        - name: crash-dumps\n          mountPath: /tmp/dumps\n  volumes:\n    - name: crash-dumps\n      emptyDir:\n        sizeLimit: 2Gi   # adjust based on your app's memory footprint\n```\n\n**Key points for NativeAOT specifically:**\n\n- `DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath` is **required** — NativeAOT doesn't bundle or auto-locate `createdump` like CoreCLR does.\n- `DOTNET_EnableCrashReport=1` writes a JSON crash info file alongside the dump, useful for quick triage without loading the full dump.\n- Use `emptyDir` with a `sizeLimit` so a runaway dump doesn't fill the node disk. Size it to ~1–2× your container's memory limit.\n- If you need dumps to survive pod restarts, swap `emptyDir` for a `PersistentVolumeClaim`.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"5a843b73-470b-49b5-9213-5de4f28ce81a","outputTokens":547,"requestId":"7842:1479F8:4B43DE:56AEDF:69FA9DBD"},"id":"f1b067ee-e6de-47c9-aa38-62166d3cf93b","timestamp":"2026-05-06T01:47:53.578Z","parentId":"da8cd6ab-54d5-4c9f-9a51-57d61a9a1572"}
